Package tage.nodeControllers

Class BobController

  • java.lang.Object
    • tage.NodeController
      • tage.nodeControllers.BobController
  • public class BobController
extends NodeController
    A BobController controls how much the targeted object moves up and down. It moves the targeted object up and down on a cycle. A BobController instance has fields for the direction, the speed, cycleTime, totalTime. It also includes Vector3fs for oldPosiiton, newPosition, and direction3f. It also has a field for the engine. By default, the cycle time is 2 seconds.
